Welcome to the Hunter Valley Resort


Located in the very heart of the Hunter Valley Wine Country, the Hunter Valley Resort is an easy 2 hours motorway drive north of Sydney. Alternatively, come by train and we will pick you up from the local Singleton railway station.


We are not one of those 'big' international chain resorts, rather a family owned and operated country inn or lodge with 35 rooms and cottages, nestled within our own 45 year old shiraz vineyards on 70 secluded acres.


More than just a place to stay, onsite are many activities and facilities: 




* Dining - Italian Bites, Pizza & Pasta; 



* A range of great guestrooms and cottages; 



* 38 wines from 8 local producers, including our own great wines to sample from our Wine Tasting Cellars; 



* Matilda Bay Brewhouse with 12 craft brews; 



* The Hunter Wine Theatre; 



* Wine & Cooking Schools; 



* Candy and Pizza making classes; 



* Winery where guests can learn how the wine is made; 



* Horseriding adventures; 



* Segway kangaroo spotting and nature tours; 



* Dessert bar & gourmet produce; 



* Heavenly Hunter massage centre


Adjacent to us is the Binnorie Cheese Dairy and just down the road are:




* 4 championship golf courses, 



* Skydiving, 



* Hot Air Ballooning, 



* Hunter Valley Gardens + Shopping Village, 



* Hunter Distillery 



* Over 140 wineries to visit.
Source: this is an extract from the company’s own website.
